        "content": "<p>The page size on wasm is 64k. There is a wasm proposal to allow using smaller page sizes though: <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes\">https://github.com/WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes</a> I think WAMR doesn't support it yet though.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes\" title=\"GitHub - WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes\">GitHub - WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Contribute to WebAssembly/custom-page-sizes development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
